```json
{
  "application": "LAMMPS",
  "details": {
    "modules": [
      "yaff/1.0.develop.2.14-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10-HDF5-1.8.15-patch1-serial",
      "LAMMPS/r12824-intel-2015b",
      "mpi4py/2.0.0-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10",
      "vsc-mympirun/3.4.2-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10-vsc-base-2.4.2"
    ],
    "environment": {
      "VSC_DATA_VO": "path_to_vsc_data",
      "VSC_SCRATCH_VO": "path_to_vsc_scratch"
    },
    "resources": {
      "nodes": 1,
      "processors_per_node": 4,
      "walltime": "72:00:00"
    },
    "scripts": {
      "ymd.py": "main python script",
      "liblammps.py": "LAMMPS library",
      "mylammps.py": "Custom LAMMPS functions",
      "lammps_smoothei2.table": "Smooth interaction potential table",
      "pars.txt": "Simulation parameters"
    },
    "commands": [
      "source $VSC_DATA_VO/vsc40685_apps/activate.sh",
      "module load yaff/1.0.develop.2.14-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10-HDF5-1.8.15-patch1-serial",
      "module load LAMMPS/r12824-intel-2015b",
      "module load mpi4py/2.0.0-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10",
      "module load vsc-mympirun/3.4.2-intel-2015b-Python-2.7.10-vsc-base-2.4.2",
      "mkdir -p $WORKDIR",
      "cp $ORIGDIR/* $WORKDIR/.",
      "cp $SCRIPTDIR/liblammps.py $WORKDIR/.",
      "cp $SCRIPTDIR/mylammps.py $WORKDIR/.",
      "cp $SCRIPTDIR/lammps_smoothei2.table $WORKDIR/.",
      "cp $SCRIPTDIR/pars.txt $WORKDIR/.",
      "cd $WORKDIR",
      "mympirun python ymd.py",
      "cp $WORKDIR/* $ORIGDIR/.",
      "rm $ORIGDIR/liblammps.py",
      "rm $ORIGDIR/mylammps.py",
      "rm $ORIGDIR/lammps_smoothei2.table",
      "rm $ORIGDIR/pars.txt",
      "cd $ORIGDIR",
      "rm -rf $WORKDIR"
    ]
  }
}
```
